# Chump (this repository)

- Read **docs/ROADMAP.md**, **docs/CHUMP_PROJECT_BRIEF.md**, and **AGENTS.md** before substantive work. Human checklist: **CONTRIBUTING.md**.
- **Before you finish:** `cargo fmt --all -- --check`, `cargo test --workspace`, `cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings` (same as CI — see **CONTRIBUTING.md**).
- **Repo file edits:** use **`patch_file`** (single-file unified diff; read the file first) or **`write_file`** / append. There is **no `edit_file` tool** in this codebase.
- **Handoffs / fleet:** follow **`docs/CHUMP_CURSOR_FLEET.md`** (canonical Cursor CLI + multi-agent patterns). Rule: **`.cursor/rules/chump-multi-agent-fleet.mdc`**.
- **Scope:** one roadmap item or task per focused run; mark **docs/ROADMAP.md** checkboxes only when work is verified.
- **Hygiene:** `./scripts/doc-keeper.sh` checks doc links; **`doc_hygiene`** heartbeat rounds (see **docs/OPERATIONS.md**) maintain Markdown under `docs/`, **AGENTS.md**, and this folder.
- **Roadmap hub files (`docs/ROADMAP*.md`, `docs/README.md` roadmap rows):** follow **roadmap-doc-hygiene.mdc** and **docs/CURSOR_CLI_INTEGRATION.md** §3.4.
- **Secrets:** never commit `.env` or tokens; see **SECURITY.md**.
